%global python3_pkgversion 3.9

Name:    robinhood4
Version: 1.5.2
Release: 1%{?dist}
Summary: RobinHood V4 tool suite

Group:   Applications/System
License: LGPLv3
URL:     https://github.com/robinhood-suite/robinhood4.git
Source0: %{name}-%{version}.tar.xz

# build options    || .rpmmacros options || change to default action
# =================  ====================  ===========================
# --with hestia    || %%_with_hestia 1   || build hestia plugin
# --with ldiskfs   || %%_with_ldiskfs 1  || build ldiskfs plugin
# --without lustre || %%_with_lustre 0   || don't build lustre extension
# --without man    || %%_with_man 0      || don't build man pages
# --with mfu       || %%_with_mfu 1      || build mfu plugin and extension
# --without mongo  || %%_with_mongo 0    || don't build mongo plugin
# --with s3        || %%_with_s3 1       || build s3 plugin

%bcond_with hestia
%bcond_with ldiskfs
%bcond_without lustre
%bcond_without man
%bcond_with mfu
%bcond_without mongo
%bcond_with s3

Conflicts: robinhood

Requires: miniyaml
Requires: python39
Requires: python3-yaml

BuildRequires: meson
BuildRequires: gcc
BuildRequires: jansson-devel
BuildRequires: check-devel
BuildRequires: glib2-devel
BuildRequires: libuuid-devel
BuildRequires: libyaml-devel
BuildRequires: pkgconf-pkg-config
BuildRequires: miniyaml-devel
BuildRequires: python39
BuildRequires: python3-rpm-macros
BuildRequires: python3-devel
BuildRequires: python3-sphinx

%description
The RobinHood4 tool suite. Includes librobinhood and the POSIX plugin, rbh-sync,
rbh-fsevents, rbh-find, rbh-report, rbh-info, rbh-gc, rbh-update-path,
rbh-undelete, rbh-update-retention and rbh-policy.

%package devel
Summary: C API for RobinHood V4 tool suite.
Conflicts: robinhood
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: pkgconf-pkg-config

%description devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the robinhood4 tool
suite from a C program.

%package client-retention
Summary: Userland tools for RobinHood V4 tool suite.

%description client-retention
This package contains the rbh-retention tool for usage by regular (non-admin)
users.

%if %{with hestia}
%package hestia
Summary: Hestia plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: hestia
BuildRequires: hestia-devel

%description hestia
The Hestia plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by rbh-sync and
rbh-fsevents.

%package hestia-devel
Summary: C API of the Ldiskfs plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-hestia
Requires: hestia-devel

%description hestia-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the Hestia plugin from
a C program.
%endif

%if %{with ldiskfs}
%package ldiskfs
Summary: Ldiskfs plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: lustre-client
BuildRequires: lustre-devel

%description ldiskfs
The ldiskfs plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by rbh-sync.

%package ldiskfs-devel
Summary: C API of the Ldiskfs plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-ldiskfs
Requires: lustre-devel

%description ldiskfs-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the ldiskfs plugin from
a C program.
%endif

%if %{with mfu}
%package mfu
Summary: MPI-File-Utils plugin and POSIX extension for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: openmpi
Requires: libmfu
BuildRequires: openmpi-devel
BuildRequires: libmfu-devel

%description mfu
The MPI-File plugin and MFU extension for POSIX for the RobinHood V4 tool suite,
usable by rbh-sync and rbh-find.

%package mfu-devel
Summary: C API of the MPI-File-Utils plugin and POSIX extension for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-mfu
Requires: openmpi-devel
Requires: libmfu-devel

%description mfu-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the mpi-file plugin and
MFU extension for POSIX from a C program.
%endif

%if %{with mongo}
%package mongo
Summary: MongoDB plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: mongo-c-driver-libs
# The MongoDB dependency can be found here: https://repo.mongo.org/yum/redhat/
Requires: (mongo-org or mongo)
BuildRequires: mongo-c-driver-devel

%description mongo
The MongoDB plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by all tools.

%package mongo-devel
Summary: C API of the MongoDB plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-mongo
Requires: mongo-c-driver-devel

%description mongo-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the MongoDB plugin from
a C program.
%endif

%if %{with lustre}
%package posix-lustre
Summary: Lustre extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: lustre-client
# Should be the following line, but there is currently an issue with repository
# priority and yum that makes it so that lustre-client is always used if
# available, completely ignoring lustre-devel
#BuildRequires: (lustre-devel or lustre-client < 2.15)
BuildRequires: lustre-devel

%description posix-lustre
The Lustre plugin for POSIX for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by multiple
tools.

%package posix-lustre-devel
Summary: C API of the lustre extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-posix-lustre
#Requires: (lustre-devel or lustre-client < 2.15)
Requires: lustre-devel

%description posix-lustre-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the Lustre extension
for POSIX from a C program.
%endif

%package posix-retention
Summary: Retention extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2

%description posix-retention
The Retention plugin for POSIX for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by
multiple tools.

%package posix-retention-devel
Summary: C API of the retention extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-posix-retention

%description posix-retention-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the Retention extension
for POSIX from a C program.

%package posix-sparse
Summary: Sparse extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2

%description posix-sparse
The Sparse plugin for POSIX for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by rbh-sync
and rbh-find.

%package posix-sparse-devel
Summary: C API of the sparse extension of the POSIX plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-posix-sparse

%description posix-sparse-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the Sparse extension
for POSIX from a C program.

%if %{with s3}
%package s3
Summary: S3 plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4 == 1.5.2
Requires: aws-cpp-sdk-s3

%description s3
The S3 plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite, usable by rbh-sync and rbh-find.

%package s3-devel
Summary: C API of the S3 plugin for the RobinHood V4 tool suite
Requires: robinhood4-devel
Requires: robinhood4-s3

%description s3-devel
This package contains header files and libraries to use the S3 plugin from a C
program.
%endif

%prep
%autosetup

%build
OPTS=""
%if %{with hestia}
    OPTS+="-Dhestia=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dhestia=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with ldiskfs}
    OPTS+="-Dldiskfs=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dldiskfs=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with lustre}
    OPTS+="-Dlustre=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dlustre=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with man}
    OPTS+="-Dman=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dman=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with mfu}
    OPTS+="-Dmfu=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dmfu=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with mongo}
    OPTS+="-Dmongo=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Dmongo=disabled "
%endif

%if %{with s3}
    OPTS+="-Ds3=enabled "
%else
    OPTS+="-Ds3=disabled "
%endif

%meson $OPTS
%meson_build

%install
%meson_install

%files
%{_libdir}/librobinhood.so*
%{_libdir}/librbh-posix.so*
%{_libdir}/pkgconfig/robinhood.pc
%{_bindir}/rbh-sync
%{_bindir}/rbh-find
%{_bindir}/rbh-info
%if %{with lustre}
%{_bindir}/rbh-undelete
%endif
%{_bindir}/rbh-update-retention
%{python3_sitelib}/rbhupdateretention/*
%{_bindir}/rbh-report
%{_bindir}/rbh-gc
%{_bindir}/rbh-update-path
%{_bindir}/rbh-policy
%{python3_sitelib}/rbhpolicy/*
%if %{with man}
%{_mandir}/man1/*
%{_mandir}/man5/*
%{_mandir}/man7/*
%endif

%config(noreplace) %{_sysconfdir}/robinhood4.d/default.yaml

%files devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/action.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/alias.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backend.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/common.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/posix.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/posix_extension.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/config.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/filter.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/filters/core.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/filters/parser.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/fsentry.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/fsevent.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/hashmap.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/id.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/iterator.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/itertools.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/list.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/mpi_rc.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/open.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/plugin.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/plugins/backend.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/plugins/common_ops.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/policyengine/actions.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/policyengine/core.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/policyengine/python.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/policyengine/trigger.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/projection.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/queue.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/ring.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/ringr.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/serialization.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/sstack.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/stack.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/statx.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/uri.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/utils.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/value.h

%files client-retention
%{_bindir}/rbh-retention
%config(noreplace) %{_sysconfdir}/robinhood4.d/default.yaml

%if %{with hestia}
%files hestia
%{_libdir}/librbh-hestia.so*

%files hestia-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/hestia.h
%endif

%if %{with ldiskfs}
%files ldiskfs
%{_libdir}/librbh-ldiskfs.so*

%files ldiskfs-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/ldiskfs.h
%endif

%if %{with mfu}
%files mfu
%{_libdir}/librbh-posix-mfu-ext.so*
%{_libdir}/librbh-mpi-file.so*

%files mfu-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/mfu.h
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/mpi_file.h
%endif

%if %{with mongo}
%files mongo
%{_libdir}/librbh-mongo.so*

%files mongo-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/mongo.h
%endif

%if %{with lustre}
%files posix-lustre
%{_libdir}/librbh-posix-lustre-ext.so*

%files posix-lustre-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/lustre.h
%endif

%files posix-retention
%{_libdir}/librbh-posix-retention-ext.so*

%files posix-retention-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/retention.h

%files posix-sparse
%{_libdir}/librbh-posix-sparse-ext.so*

%files posix-sparse-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/sparse.h

%if %{with s3}
%files s3
%{_libdir}/librbh-s3.so*

%files s3-devel
%{_includedir}/robinhood/backends/s3.h
%endif

%post
ldconfig

%changelog
* Thu Apr 30 2026 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.5.2-1
- Add ldiskfs as available backend
- Fix issue with in map searching

* Mon Apr 20 2026 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.5.1-1
- Add missing commands and python modules
- New Sparse enricher for POSIX
- Added a --version to all commands

* Wed Mar 25 2026 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.5-2
- Build man pages by default in spec file

* Mon Mar 02 2026 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.5-1
- New SQLite plugin for smaller DB setup
- New MPI iterator for S3
- Added specific filters and actions for S3 in rbh-find
- Added support for project-id metadata and associated filter
- Added multiple Lustre filters
- Man pages are now available
- New rbh-update-path tool to update the path of all entries under a directory
after a change to its name
- New rbh-gc tool to clear entries kept in the mirror backend that aren't
available anymore in the original backend
- Start of the ldiskfs plugin for directly reading a Lustre MDT, still a
work-in-progress
- Start of the rbh-policy tool for a policy engine, still a work-in-progress

* Mon Oct 20 2025 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.4-1
- New S3 plugin
- Improved performance of rbh-find/report by using projections
- Added parallelization of enrichment/update in rbh-fsevents
- Added new tool "rbh-undelete" to recreate deleted entries that were previously
archived
- Modified rbh-fsevents to do continuous acknowledgement of changelogs
- Modified rbh-fsevents to allow starting at the last index read in multi-reader
situations

* Wed May 14 2025 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.3-1
- Reorganized plugins and backends with extensions. Removed the following
backends: Lustre-MPI and POSIX-MPI. Added the following extensions to the POSIX
plugin: Lustre, Retention and MFU
- Removed the retention feature from the Lustre plugin, now a POSIX extension
instead
- Renamed rbh-capabilities to rbh-info
- Removed the rbh-find library and rbh-find-lustre tool, as Lustre filters can
now be used with rbh-find instead
- Added filtering to rbh-report
- Added new "client-retention" package that will contain the rbh-retention tool
for client/user nodes

* Wed Dec 18 2024 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.2-1
- Added rbh-report tool to retrieve aggregated information about the mirror
system

* Fri Oct 25 2024 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.1-1
- Added xattrs type configuration with the configuration file
- Added configuration parameter for rbh-update-retention
- Support new filters in rbh-find-lustre

* Tue Jul 23 2024 - Yoann Valeri <yoann.valeri@cea.fr> - 1.0-1
- First version of RobinHood V4
- Support the following backends: POSIX, Lustre, Mongo, Lustre-MPI and POSIX-MPI
and MPI file
- Provide the tools: rbh-sync, rbh-find, rbh-find-lustre, rbh-fsevents,
rbh-capabilities and rbh-update-retention
